column2: select top # P.objID, P.ra as sdss_ra, P.dec as sdss_dec, W.ra as wise_ra, W.dec as wise_dec, P.psfmag_r, W.w1mpro, P.cModelMag_u, P.cModelMagErr_u, P.cModelMag_g, P.cModelMagErr_g, P.cModelMag_r, P.cModelMagErr_r, P.cModelMag_i, P.cModelMagErr_i, P.cModelMag_z, P.cModelMagErr_z, P.modelMag_u, P.modelMagErr_u, P.modelMag_g, P.modelMagErr_g, P.modelMag_r, P.modelMagErr_r, P.modelMag_i, P.modelMagErr_i, P.modelMag_z, P.modelMagErr_z, P.petroMag_u, P.expAB_u, P.expAB_g, P.expAB_r, P.expAB_i, P.expAB_z into mydb.b from wise_xmatch as X join wise_allsky as W on X.wise_cntr = W.cntr join photoObj as P on X.sdss_objid = P.objid where P.nchild = # and P.dec between # and # SELECT a.*, b.* FROM mydb.a CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (a.ra, a.dec, #) b
